\begin_layout Standard
This section offers a non-exhaustive review of the literature on gender
 and agriculture.
 Specific emphasis is placed on the gendered dimensions of intra-household
 asymmetries of information and role models, drawing on examples that highlight
 their influence on technology adoption and extension service provision.
 
